project:
W, A, S, D - Move
V - Shoot
X - Place Mine
resetscore - Restarts the Score of both teams.
infmines - Gives both players infinite mines.
inftime - Makes the time infinite. (this can be overwritten via the endgame cheat)
killall - Deletes both players from the game. This will mess up your game.
Level up to view all cheats. All are unlocked, but you must level up to find out the cheats. Level up by playing 1v1 matches.
